{"id":39381,"artworks":[{"id":176119,"image_id":"ar3rw7"},{"id":176120,"image_id":"ar3rw8"}],"cover":{"id":467695,"image_id":"coa0vj","url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/coa0vj.jpg"},"first_release_date":794016000,"genres":[{"id":4,"name":"Fighting"},{"id":8,"name":"Platform"}],"involved_companies":[{"id":326450,"company":{"id":263,"name":"Namco"},"developer":true,"publisher":true}],"name":"The Outfoxies","release_dates":[{"id":204294,"date":794016000,"human":"Mar 01, 1995","platform":{"id":52,"name":"Arcade"},"release_region":{"id":5,"region":"japan"}}],"screenshots":[{"id":1570075,"image_id":"scxnh7","url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/scxnh7.jpg"},{"id":1570076,"image_id":"scxnh8","url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/scxnh8.jpg"},{"id":1570077,"image_id":"scxnh9","url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/scxnh9.jpg"},{"id":1570078,"image_id":"scxnha","url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/scxnha.jpg"},{"id":1570079,"image_id":"scxnhb","url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/scxnhb.jpg"},{"id":1570080,"image_id":"scxnhc","url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/scxnhc.jpg"},{"id":1570072,"image_id":"scxnh4","url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/scxnh4.jpg"},{"id":1570073,"image_id":"scxnh5","url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/scxnh5.jpg"},{"id":1570074,"image_id":"scxnh6","url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/scxnh6.jpg"},{"id":1570081,"image_id":"scxnhd","url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/scxnhd.jpg"},{"id":1570082,"image_id":"scxnhe","url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/scxnhe.jpg"},{"id":1570083,"image_id":"scxnhf","url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/scxnhf.jpg"},{"id":1570084,"image_id":"scxnhg","url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/scxnhg.jpg"}],"similar_games":[89550,96452,101608,20342,55173,24426,109277,28070,76852,55190],"slug":"the-outfoxies","summary":"The gameplay has you thrown into a particular hitman's home turf and you must use every weapon imaginable as well as anything you can find in the environment (including the environment itself) to try to kill your competitor. Weapons can be typical like a rocket launcher or machine gun or absurd like a clown cannon or a bowl of hot soup. Despite dealing with a competition about murder, the game has a levity to it in all aspects.\n\nThe levels are also a star part of this game as they are varied and, in many cases, will begin to collapse as time goes on. This means that if the player doesn't kill his competition in a set amount of time the level will literally start crumbling around you. The levels take place in various interactive locations, involving inside a plane, a moving train, an office building or even at the circus.","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/the-outfoxies","websites":[{"id":339383,"url":"https://www.twitch.tv/directory/game/The%20Outfoxies","type":{"id":6,"type":"Twitch"}}]}